headline: Assessing Fifth Third Bancorp (FITB) Valuation After Strong Recent Share Price Momentum
summary: Fifth Third Bancorp (FITB) has drawn fresh attention after recent share moves, with the stock showing double digit returns over the past month and over the past three months. That performance is prompting closer scrutiny of its fundamentals. See our latest analysis for Fifth Third Bancorp. These recent share price moves build on a longer run, with the stock showing a 27.15% 3 month share price return and a 27.47% 1 year total shareholder return, which points to sustained positive momentum...
